<li id="cite_note-Florian.2CMikulincer.2CBucholtz.2C1995-58"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Florian.2CMikulincer.2CBucholtz.2C1995_58-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFFlorian_V.2C_Mikulincer_M.2C_Bucholtz_I1995">Florian V, Mikulincer M, Bucholtz I (November 1995). "Effects of adult attachment style on the perception and search for social support". <i>J Psychol</i> <b>129</b> (6): 665–76. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/7500299" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/7500299">PMID 7500299</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Effects+of+adult+attachment+style+on+the+perception+and+search+for+social+support&amp;rft.jtitle=J+Psychol&amp;rft.aulast=Florian+V%2C+Mikulincer+M%2C+Bucholtz+I&amp;rft.au=Florian+V%2C+Mikulincer+M%2C+Bucholtz+I&amp;rft.date=November+1995&amp;rft.volume=129&amp;rft.issue=6&amp;rft.pages=665%E2%80%9376&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/7500299&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Attachment_in_adults"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
